<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" ?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:s="https://admin.wvusports.com/services/xml_schema/story" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/"><channel><title>West Virginia University Athletics</title><link>https://admin.wvusports.com/rss.aspx</link><description>Latest news items for West Virginia University Athletics</description><atom:link href="https://admin.wvusports.com/rss" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" /><language>en-us</language><ttl>60</ttl><item><title>Golf Team Continues Play in Georgia</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/12/golf-team-continues-play-in-georgia</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/12/golf-team-continues-play-in-georgia</guid><category>Golf</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Schenkel" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/12/GOLF_2025Matchup_1920x1080_.png" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University golf team will wrap up its week in Georgia this weekend by competing in the Schenkel Invitational in Statesboro, Georgia.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/12/GOLF_2025Matchup_1920x1080_.png" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/12/GOLF_2025Matchup_1920x1080_.png"><media:title>Schenkel</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/12/GOLF_2025Matchup_1920x1080_.png" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 12:03:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>5</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58852</s:story_id></item><item><title>WVU Looks to Claim Program Second Straight NCAA Rifle National Championship</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/12/wvu-looks-to-claim-program-second-straight-ncaa-rifle-national-championship</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/12/wvu-looks-to-claim-program-second-straight-ncaa-rifle-national-championship</guid><category>Rifle</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Oceanne Muller" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/11/_LPA7015.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The No. 4-seeded West Virginia University rifle team looks to capture its nation-best 21th national championship this weekend, as the Mountaineers get set to conclude their season at the 2026 NCAA Rifle Championships from March 13-14, in Columbus, Ohio.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/11/_LPA7015.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/11/_LPA7015.jpg"><media:title>Oceanne Muller</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/11/_LPA7015.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 12:00:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>8</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58844</s:story_id></item><item><title>West Virginia Caps Regular Season with Double Meet Weekend</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/12/gymnastics-west-virginia-caps-regular-season-with-double-meet-weekend</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/12/gymnastics-west-virginia-caps-regular-season-with-double-meet-weekend</guid><category>Gymnastics</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="amber lowe" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/12/VVB07181.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University gymnastics team is set for its final weekend of the regular season with a pair of meets on the road, beginning at No. 21 NC State on Friday, March 13. Competition inside the James T. Valvano Arena at William Neal Reynolds Coliseum in Raleigh, N.C., is set for 6 p.m. ET. The weekend then concludes in a tri meet at Pitt on Sunday, March 15. Illinois State will join the Mountaineers at the meet, which is scheduled for 2 p.m., at Fitzgerald Field House in Pittsburgh, Pa.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/12/VVB07181.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/12/VVB07181.jpg"><media:title>amber lowe</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/12/VVB07181.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Thu, 12 Mar 2026 10:56:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>11</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58851</s:story_id></item><item><title>Hellmann Qualifies for First NCAA Swimming and Diving Championships</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/11/mens-swimming-diving-hellmann-qualifies-for-first-ncaa-swimming-and-diving-championships</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/11/mens-swimming-diving-hellmann-qualifies-for-first-ncaa-swimming-and-diving-championships</guid><category>Men's Swimming &amp; Diving, Women's Swimming &amp; Diving</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Levi Hellmann at 2026 Big 12 Championships (Feb. 24, 2026)" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/2/25/DSC06432.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – Sophomore Levi Hellmann is heading to his first NCAA Swimming and Diving Championships after placing fourth on platform at the NCAA Zone A Diving Championships on Wednesday at Lejeune Hall in Annapolis, Maryland.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/2/25/DSC06432.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/2/25/DSC06432.jpg"><media:title>Levi Hellmann at 2026 Big 12 Championships (Feb. 24, 2026)</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/2/25/DSC06432.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 17:11:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>7</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58848</s:story_id></item><item><title>NCAA Releases Brackets for 2026 NCAA Wrestling Championships</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/11/ncaa-releases-brackets-for-2026-ncaa-wrestling-championships</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/11/ncaa-releases-brackets-for-2026-ncaa-wrestling-championships</guid><category>Wrestling</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="No alternative text provided." src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2025/10/14/flynn-tim_4.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The brackets for the 2026 NCAA Wrestling Championships have been released, setting the stage for the tournament that begins on March 19 at Rocket Arena in Cleveland, Ohio.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2025/10/14/flynn-tim_4.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2025/10/14/flynn-tim_4.jpg"><media:title /></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/imag