3/11/Mark2_Main.jpg"><media:title>Mark Kellogg</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/11/Mark2_Main.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 15:14:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>9</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58846</s:story_id></item><item><title>Mountaineers Travel to Face No. 42 Utah, No. 45 BYU</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/11/tennis-mountaineers-travel-to-face-no-42-utah-no-45-byu</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/11/tennis-mountaineers-travel-to-face-no-42-utah-no-45-byu</guid><category>Tennis</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Laura Villanueva Morillo" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/11/ex1_1_copy_2.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University tennis team (6-5, 0-4 Big 12) continues Big 12 Conference play with a two match road trip this week, beginning at No. 42 Utah (8-5, 1-2 Big 12) on Thursday, March 12, at 5 p.m. before traveling to take on No. 45 BYU (11-4, 0-3 Big 12) on Saturday, March 14, at 1 p.m.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/11/ex1_1_copy_2.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/11/ex1_1_copy_2.jpg"><media:title>Laura Villanueva Morillo</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/11/ex1_1_copy_2.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Wed, 11 Mar 2026 12:00:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>15</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58845</s:story_id></item><item><title>West Virginia Tips off Big 12 Tournament Play on Wednesday Night</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/10/mens-basketball-west-virginia-tips-off-big-12-tournament-play-on-wednesday-night</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/3/10/mens-basketball-west-virginia-tips-off-big-12-tournament-play-on-wednesday-night</guid><category>Men's Basketball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Honor Huff" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/3/10/Huff-Main.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – West Virginia begins Phillips 66 Big 12 Championship play at T-Mobile Center in Kansas City on Wednesday night against 10th-seeded BYU, which defeated 15th-seeded Kansas State 105-91 on Tuesday.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/10/Huff-Main.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/10/Huff-Main.jpg"><media:title>Honor Huff</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/3/10/Huff-Main.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 21:12:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>4</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58843</s:story_id></item></channel></rss>